Wait a minute. Wait a minute.

00:28:03.643 --> 00:28:08.056
671... now.

00:28:09.983 --> 00:28:13.443
And that's the one, Marvin.
That's the silver tuna.

00:28:13.444 --> 00:28:15.654
Oh, it's very "G."

