member of his immediate family?

00:32:53.933 --> 00:32:58.020
- No.
- Has he been involved in a household accident?

00:32:58.021 --> 00:33:00.355
I don't know. I don't...
I hope not.

00:33:00.356 --> 00:33:02.941
Has the child ingested any poison...

00:33:02.942 --> 00:33:05.736
and/or any other object that has become
lodged in his throat?

00:33:05.737 --> 00:33:09.448
No, he's just home alone! I would like
somebody to go over to the house...

00:33:09.449 --> 00:33:12.367
and see that he's all right,
just to check on him.

00:33:12.368 --> 00:33:16.121
You want us to go to your house
just to check on him?

00:33:16.122 --> 00:33:16.831
Yes!

00:33:16.832 --> 00:33:19.625
Let me connect you with
the police department.

00:33:19.626 --> 00:33:22.252
- They just transferred me to you.
- Rose?

00:33:22.253 --> 00:33:24.796
- Yeah?
- Hyper on two. Hold on, please.

00:33:24.797 --> 00:33:28.800
No, please don't hang up.
Please, don't... Any luck?

00:33:28.801 --> 00:33:32.554
No. We couldn't get anybody.

00:33:32.555 --> 00:33:33.339
Leslie?

00:33:33.340 --> 00:33:36.576
I'm sorry, Kate. Nothing but a
bunch of answering machines.

00:33:38.603 --> 00:33:42.314
Somebody pick up.
Pick up!

