00:38:24.597 --> 00:38:25.415
Yeah?

00:38:25.416 --> 00:38:28.684
House we were at last night,
was that the McCallisters?

00:38:28.685 --> 00:38:31.228
- Yeah.
- Call me in Paris.

00:38:31.229 --> 00:38:33.973
You're right. They're gone.

00:38:37.193 --> 00:38:40.229
- I knew they were.
- Silver tuna tonight.

00:38:42.198 --> 00:38:44.358
Wow.

00:38:49.289 --> 00:38:51.373
How may I help you?

