Is this toothbrush approved
by the American Dental Association?

00:38:55.295 --> 00:38:58.213
Well, I don't know.

00:38:58.214 --> 00:39:02.168
- It doesn't say, hon.
- Can you please find out?

00:39:04.971 --> 00:39:07.097
- Herb!
- Yeah?

00:39:07.098 --> 00:39:11.094
I've got a question here
about a toothbrush.

00:39:16.441 --> 00:39:20.819
Do you know, is this toothbrush approved
by the American Dental Association?

00:39:20.820 --> 00:39:22.939
I don't know.

00:39:43.593 --> 00:39:48.096
- Just tell him that...
- Oh, hon, you pay for that here.

00:39:48.097 --> 00:39:50.098
Why don't you just
tell him it's approved?

00:39:50.099 --> 00:39:53.519
Wait, son, you have to pay
for that toothbrush. Son?

00:39:53.520 --> 00:39:55.604
Son! Hey!

00:39:55.605 --> 00:39:59.517
Jimmy! Stop that boy!

00:40:02.779 --> 00:40:06.274
Hey! Hey!

00:40:08.034 --> 00:40:09.986
Shoplifter!

00:40:13.039 --> 00:40:14.998
Hey! Hey, kid!

