00:42:14.828 --> 00:42:16.245
I can do it if I want to.

00:42:16.246 --> 00:42:19.122
- You're sick.
- I'm not sick.

00:42:19.123 --> 00:42:22.410
- Hey, watch out!

00:42:28.716 --> 00:42:32.427
Hey. Hey! You gotta watch out
for traffic, son, you know?

00:42:32.428 --> 00:42:34.930
- Sorry.
- Damn.

00:42:34.931 --> 00:42:37.307
Santy don't visit
the funeral homes, little buddy.

00:42:37.308 --> 00:42:39.601
Okay, okay.

00:42:39.602 --> 00:42:43.097
Merry Christmas.

